WEBVTT

00:03:28.799 --> 00:03:30.238
despite their extreme poverty,

00:03:30.262 --> 00:03:32.639
placed great value
on their health and well-being.

00:03:32.663 --> 00:03:35.113
They were absolutely not poor in mind.

00:03:35.137 --> 00:03:38.138
As with all of us, they would appreciate
a well-designed product

00:03:38.162 --> 00:03:39.594
developed for their needs.

00:03:40.250 --> 00:03:42.747
After many iterations
working with experts,

00:03:42.771 --> 00:03:44.252
medical health professionals

00:03:44.276 --> 00:03:46.111
and the women themselves,

00:03:46.135 --> 00:03:49.503
I should say it was not
an easy process at all,

00:03:49.527 --> 00:03:52.433
but we had a simple and beautiful design.

00:03:53.687 --> 00:03:58.457
For a dollar more than what
the existing product was offered for,

00:03:58.481 --> 00:04:01.232
at three dollars, we were able
to deliver "janma,"